        "type": "text",
        "title": "The Logotype",
        "text": "The logo is inspired by the brand’s name and its history. It’s based on the familiar look of a highway exit sign—specifically the one the founder used to take. We combined that nostalgic feeling with a modern design to create something both classic and new.",
