        "type": "text",
        "title": "Visual Language",
        "text": "We blended road elements with marketing themes to show the \"journey\" of a B2B marketer. We turned U.S. road signs into icons and used road imagery as a main theme. It’s an invitation for marketers to take the \"Exit Five turn\" to find new opportunities in their careers.",
